headDescription: FETISHGROUND is a electronic music project by ONE 0000 0001
pageHeaderImageAlt: Fleshware with a gasmask for the header image
sectionTextP: I started composing for this project in 2007 as Fleshware. It took me years to create the seventeen tracks of my debut album 'A la recherche de soi-même...'. I qualify this album 'A la recherche de soi-même...' as Oppressiv Elektro Pop.
After this album, I made some more experimental experimental ambiant EP.
I, as ONE 0000 0001, currently rework or make a video for each track of the album 'A la recherche de soi-même...'.
